502
00:40:09,890 --> 00:40:11,470
Zapravo, umreš zbog
dehidracije.

503
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:14,220
Znaci, grozno je i bolno.

504
00:40:15,520 --> 00:40:16,480
Ali relativno brzo.

505
00:40:19,230 --> 00:40:19,940
Laku noc.

506
00:40:47,210 --> 00:40:48,630
Prilicno nezgodno.

507
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,010
Pomislio sam da bi vi
i vaša supruga...

508
00:40:51,140 --> 00:40:52,930
