567
00:47:04,380 --> 00:47:06,430
Lokalni trgovac kojeg
znam putuje u petak.

568
00:47:08,300 --> 00:47:09,260
Townsend.

569
00:47:10,390 --> 00:47:11,140
Charlie Townsend?

