622
00:54:05,930 --> 00:54:07,850
Došao sam u bungalov
i naišao na vas...

623
00:54:09,220 --> 00:54:12,600
...krhku i umornu...

624
00:54:13,600 --> 00:54:14,610
...i vrlo nesretnu.

625
00:54:16,360 --> 00:54:17,440
Bilo je to dugo putovanje.

626
00:54:18,360 --> 00:54:19,690
Ali i sad ste nesretni.

627
00:54:22,450 --> 00:54:23,860
I palo mi je na pamet da se vi

628
00:54:23,950 --> 00:54:25,910
