01:58:23,040 --> 01:58:23,950
Zaista?

1162
01:58:25,500 --> 01:58:26,620
Mislim da si u pravu.

1163
01:58:29,340 --> 01:58:30,290
Hajdemo.

1164
01:58:33,420 --> 01:58:35,550
Bolje da požurimo.
Djed nas ceka.

1165
01:58:39,970 --> 01:58:40,800
Kitty Fane?

1166
01:58:44,810 --> 01:58:46,230
Za ne povjerovati!

1167
01:58:46,640 --> 01:58:47,730
Hello, Charlie.

1168
01:58:48,560 --> 01:58:49,730
Što radiš u Londonu?

1169
01:58:53,230 --> 01:58:54,900
Znam, prošlo je puno vremena.

1170
01:58:56,820 --> 01:58:57,860
Trebao sam ti pisati.

1171
01:59:01,200 --> 01:59:03,330
Tko je ova momcina?
Zdravo, mladicu.

1172
01:59:03,790 --> 01:59:05,960
Kako se zoveš?
Walter.

1173
01:59:06,040 --> 01:59:09,630
Zdravo, Waltere. Ja sam
Charlie Townsend.

1174
01:59:11,130 --> 01:59:12,130
Koliko ti je godina?

1175
01:59:12,500 --> 01:59:13,380
Pet.

1176
01:59:14,050 --> 01:59:16,800
Hajdemo, dušo. Zaista bi
se trebali požuriti.

1177
01:59:17,130 --> 01:59:18,180
Da, naravno.

1178
01:59:19,260 --> 01:59:22,220
Pa, bilo je divno
sresti te opet.

1179
01:59:25,560 --> 01:59:26,640
Zbogom, Waltere.

1180
01:59:26,890 --> 01:59:27,890
Zbogom.

1181
01:59:32,400 --> 01:59:33,190
Kitty!

1182
01:59:34,900 --> 01:59:36,190
Bit cu u Londonu slijedeca
tri tjedna. Možda

1183
01:59:36,190 --> 01:59:38,110
bismo mogli...
Zbogom, Gospodine Townsend.

1184
01:59:40,570 --> 01:59:41,570
Zbogom, Gðo Fane.

1185
01:59:45,660 --> 01:59:46,700
Mama, tko je to bio?

1186
01:59:48,250 --> 01:59:49,710
Nitko važan, dušo.

1187
02:04:02,250 --> 02:04:05,920
U znak sjecanja na naše
prijatelje JULIE PEARCE

1188
02:04:05,960 --> 02:04:07,840
i JOHN TIMPERLEY

